（印度式餃子）同埋咖哩角（個名唔記得）因為其他印度野都唔啱香港人食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T10:08:05.000Z","msg":"Momo係尼泊爾餃子<br />\n<br />\n印度素食非精彩，我鍾意yellow dal fry（黃扁豆）aloo gobi（aloo係薯仔，gobi係椰菜花）paneer makhani （makhani 係用蕃茄煮嘅印度芝士）"},{"pid":"1a29acdbbc61cb038c11ca5f834b0c29da840e89","tid":2482394,"uid":277816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"178dfa6fea14a8034757f294d678f51037d2b5d9","tid":2482394,"uid":262611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6151164ee83bf569ca44d3459d33382c6c0399b1","tid":2482394,"uid":75196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T02:57:15.000Z","msg":"港島區有冇推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"New Punjab !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T10:08:40.000Z","msg":"Bombay Dream<br />\nJojo"},{"pid":"ae2c9479997b090250f9c4c87da29961cd719d1f","tid":2482394,"uid":277816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b32a63ca25529dace8622f984a61c2c09ae80bd","tid":2482394,"uid":7311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"536623ff590155b9140579f2714dddfa99402e67","tid":2482394,"uid":262611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cd3fb213dcfd8011f1a3b050341dc305dfb80b6b","tid":2482394,"uid":7311,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T02:59:30.000Z","msg":"做印度公司食素個啲印度同事<br />\nlunch會叫啲印度人整ge外賣<br />\n好鬼多豆 啲米都同香港人食開唔同<br />\n<br />\n佢地如果係印度出完trip番嚟買個啲零食甜到死 冇香港人會死<br />\n<br />\n經過多年試驗佢哋買散水餅會買momo（印度式餃子）同埋咖哩角（個名唔記得）因為其他印度野都唔啱香港人食<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T03:04:31.000Z","msg":"有時都好奇local食開既curry係咪會重口味好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T03:12:45.000Z","msg":"同香港個啲好唔同